$BR
\( y_p(t) = \) \{ ans_rule(40) \}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("formulas") \}

$ITEMSEP
$ITEM  Find the total solution, \( y(t) \) for the initial condition \( y(0)  = $y0 \) and \( y'(0)  = $ydot0 \).
$BR
\( y(t) = \) \{ ans_rule(60) \}
